    GORCHGWRoute -->|"HTTPS/8490<br/>TLS"| GORCHGWSvc
    NEMORoute -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS"| NEMOKRBP
    EvalHubRoute -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS client auth"| EvalHubSvc

